Editor-in-Chief Oikawa Shoichi.
</P>
<P>
Li said that China and Japan are neighboring countries and they
should continue their friendship for generations. He called for
governmental and non-governmental efforts in both countries,
including efforts from the press, to help achieve the goal.
</P>
<P>
