<P>
Li also answered questions on Japan's relations with the
Democratic People's Republic of Korea and the issue of Taiwan.
</P>
<P>
Shoichi said that now that the elder generation who first built
the friendship between Japan and China have passed away, the
younger generation should carry on their will to promote the
friendship. He promised that Yomiuri Shimbun will use its
advantage to contribute to the relationship. 
